<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-36-0346 </DOCNO><TEXT>The instrument described in this invention can perform simultaneous neutronactivation analysis of the components of materials containing radioisotopeswith different half-lifes. It is suitable especially for glasses andsilicates, and their starting materials. The instrument consists of anactivation unit with neutron source, sample activator and sample motiondevice, and a measuring unit. (R.P.) 2 figs.</TEXT></DOC>